OL,3,CMixed reaction to VAR introduction for
OL,4,CLeague Cup final
OL,6,FVAR - or Video Assistant Referee - is
OL,7,Fcoming to Northern Irish domestic
OL,8,Ffootball for the first time.
OL,10,FBut NIFL's announcement that the
OL,11,Fsystem will be used in the League Cup
OL,12,FFinal between Linfield and Glentoran
OL,13,Fon Sunday 15th March has been met with
OL,14,Fa mixed response from fans, managers,
OL,15,Fplayers and pundits.
OL,17,F"Probably the frustrating, surprising
OL,18,Fthing was the communication levels
OL,19,Fbefore it was announced," Linfield
OL,20,Fboss David Healy told UTV.
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@YO]
