PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773045643
OL,3,CMixed reaction to VAR introduction for
OL,4,CLeague Cup final
OL,6,F"What it meant for the cup final, how
OL,7,Fit was going to be put together."
OL,9,FGiven the other rounds of the
OL,10,Fcompetition were played without the
OL,11,Ftechnology, Glentoran First Team Coach
OL,12,FTim McCann worries it could overshadow
OL,13,Fthe final.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
