FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773045643
OL,3,CMixed reaction to VAR introduction for
OL,4,CLeague Cup final
OL,6,F"If you're going to do VAR, introduce
OL,7,FVAR, do it at the start of the season,
OL,8,Fdon't be picking a senior cup final to
OL,9,Fintroduce it and certainly sit down
OL,10,Fwith both clubs and some of the senior
OL,11,Fstaff and players and sit around the
OL,12,Ftable and say 'listen lads, we're
OL,13,Fthinking about doing this, what's your
OL,14,Fopinion?'."
OL,16,FWhile the introduction of VAR for the
OL,17,Ffinal came as a surprise for both
OL,18,Fclubs not all are against the
OL,19,Ftechnology.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
