CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773045643
OL,3,CMixed reaction to VAR introduction for
OL,4,CLeague Cup final
OL,6,F"I'm excited for it," said Healy.
OL,7,F"More often than not, whether people
OL,8,Flike it or not, VAR get it right."
OL,10,FWhile the match will be refereed by
OL,11,FIrish FA officials, the VAR technology
OL,12,Fwill be handled by overseas officials
OL,13,Fmore used with the system.
OL,15,F"My only concern would be that we are
OL,16,Fnot going to have our own referees,
OL,17,Four referees will be on the pitch so
OL,18,Fit's what happens off the pitch," said
OL,19,FHealy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@UO]oD@AOUpD@bO]wD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773045643
OL,3,CMixed reaction to VAR introduction for
OL,4,CLeague Cup final
OL,6,F"I would hope in the lead up to the
OL,7,Fgame, whoever is doing the game from
OL,8,Fthe booth do have a look, they do
OL,9,Fspeak to our head of referees to get a
OL,10,Ffeel for our league where something is
OL,11,Fprobably a yellow card in the Irish
OL,12,FLeague, or maybe not a foul in the
OL,13,FIrish League, but other leagues can
OL,14,Fslightly vary.
OL,16,F"But hopefully the main talking point
OL,17,Fis on the pitch, good moments by a
OL,18,Fplayer and we're not discussing in the
OL,19,Fdays after the game how VAR got it
OL,20,Fwrong."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
