PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773045643
OL,3,CMixed reaction to VAR introduction for
OL,4,CLeague Cup final
OL,6,FMcCann said: "It's a concern because
OL,7,Fthey don't know the league, they don't
OL,8,Fknow the individuals, they don't know
OL,9,Fthe players, they don't know what type
OL,10,Fof league it is. Every league in the
OL,11,Fworld is different.
OL,13,F"It just seems like a spur of the
OL,14,Fmoment thing that has been thrown
OL,15,Ftogether. I don't think either club is
OL,16,Fa fan of it, it seems contentious at
OL,17,Fthe very least."
